<p><b> III. Making a contribution 
</b></p>
<p>6. Contributions to the Fund should always be marked &#8220;payee: Special Fund 
established by the Optional Protocol to the Convention against Torture, account CH&#8221;. 
Payments may be made either by bank transfer (a) in United States dollars to UNOG 
General Fund, account No. 485001802, J.P. Morgan Chase Bank, 270 Park Avenue, 43rd 
floor, New York, NY 10017, United States of America (Swift code: CHAS US 33; ABA 
